text: Reichmannshausen in Unterfranken is a village in the municipality of Schonungen, in Schweinfurt, Bavaria. == Geography == Reichmannshausen is 341 meters above sea level on the Schlettach plateau. It is completely surrounded by forest. == Other websites == * Information about Reichmannshausen - In German == References == Category:Villages in Bavaria Category:Schweinfurt (district)
